data.description: This property is a standout with its sought-after features, including a generous master walk-in closet and a tranquil location in a quiet neighborhood with easy access to Hwy 29. The large private backyard boasts mature trees, and security is ensured with a top-notch security system. Inside, the house offers added convenience with a central vacuum system. Recent upgrades have given this home a fresh and modern feel, including new lower-level bedrooms, smart stainless steel kitchen appliances, and a lower-level bathroom with a relaxing whirlpool tub. Additionally, new light fixtures, landscape rock features, and commercial laminate flooring throughout the lower level for added appeal.
